Installation:
pip install selenium
pip install pytest
pip install pytest-html
pip install pytest-xdist
pip install allure-pytest
pip install openpyxl
pip install faker
pip install pytest-order



Commands:
pytest -rA -v --html=report.html --self-contained-html

pytest -rA -v --html=reports/test_report.html --self-contained-html

pytest -s -rA -v --html=reports/report.html --self-contained-html


For different Browser Command:
pytest -s -rA -v --html=reports/report.html --self-contained-html --browser firefox


To add Date and Time when saving HTML Report:
pytest -s -rA -v --html="reports/report_$(Get-Date -Format 'yyyy-MM-dd_HH-mm-ss').html" --self-contained-html


For Specific Execute Single Test File:
pytest -s -rA -v --html="reports/report_$(Get-Date -Format 'yyyy-MM-dd_HH-mm-ss').html" --self-contained-html test_cases/test_add_customer_user.py

For Parallel Execution Command:
pytest -s -rA -v --html=reports/report.html --self-contained-html -n 3



For Allure Reporting:
pytest -s -rA -v --alluredir="allure-results"


To Generate Allure Report:
allure serve allure-results


Exclude a marker (NOT condition):
pytest -v -m "not smoke"

| Command                               | Meaning                             |
| ------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------- |
| `pytest -v -m "smoke"`                | Run only smoke tests                |
| `pytest -v -m "regression"`           | Run only regression tests           |
| `pytest -v -m "smoke or regression"`  | Run both smoke and regression tests |
| `pytest -v -m "smoke and regression"` | Run only tests having both markers  |
| `pytest -v -m "not regression"`       | Run all except regression tests     |
